es get approved within a day.</div></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:22px 40px 0;\" align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#132A52\" style=\"border-radius:12px;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"{{edit_url}}\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:15px 34px;font:bold 15px Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;\">Edit my profile</a></td></tr></table></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:26px 40px 28px;\" align=\"center\"><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #DEDBD1;padding-top:16px;font:normal 11px/1.6 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#5B6270;\">Questions? Just reply to this email. \u00b7 openmentor.io</div></td></tr>\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>",
